Package com.mashery.trafficmanager.event.listener

The package contains the listener interfaces which can be implemented by the custom processors to receive event call-backs for subscribed events and callbacks to the life-cycle states of the listener.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Authenticator
    Authenticator interface which is implemented by listeners which wish to handle Authenticate events.
    LifeCycleContext
    The context passed into the lifecycle callback
    ListenerLifeCycle
    The lifecycle callback which gets called when the processor gets loaded when installed and released
    TrafficEventListener
    Event listener interface which is implemented by listeners which wish to handle Traffic events.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ListenerLifeCycleException
    Exception thrown when a lifecycle event callback fails
